metadata.name: What's beyond? #1
metadata.description:
Lucie Mudrochová - Czech Republic

This is a boxing story... Made of sweat, blood and tears. I spent hours and hours around boxing rings, as a boxer and as a photographer. As a boxer, I have tasted both the sweetness of victory, but also the bitterness of defeat. As a photographer I feel well equipped to deal with any situation, good or bad. The emotional rollercoaster going on from the locker room to the ring is extreme, it is intoxicating! I ll take you close as you ever been.
